title: CANT CHOOSE FROM FREE CHAMPION ROTATION
body: Im 10 level and i cant choose from free champ rot i can choose from start one. Why?{{champion:107}}

replies.body: The [free champion rotation ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752864-Choosing-the-Right-Champion)was recently changed.  You should see the free weekly champs in another level!
